      <p>Although technically not in Ozone Park, Forest Park is on the border with Ozone Park and worth mentioning. Goers interested in exploring Forest Park’s natural settings firsthand often travel to its eastern portion, which abounds in hiking trails and bridle paths.</p>

</p><br><br>
