      <p>2001</p>
      <p>A Bronx Tale features a scene set at Aqueduct Racetrack in Ozone Park. It is an American crime drama film, adapted from Chazz Palminteri's 1989 play of the same name. It tells the coming of age story of an Italian-American boy, Calogero Anello, who, after encountering a local Mafia boss, is torn between the temptations of organized crime and the values of his honest, hardworking father.
      </p><br><br>
      
